{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e71b2f7f0e","title":"毛远新谈对批邓和四五天安门事件的意见","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"738e1d5efd","index":0,"year":1976,"month":4,"day":19,"articleId":"e71b2f7f0e"}],"tags":[{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"b4ae0c4e82","name":"辽宁文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"f8d6ecb146","name":"毛远新","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[{"id":"d78589ea8b","name":"（四）毛远新一九七六年四月十九日谈对当前工作的意见","articleId":"e71b2f7f0e"}],"publications":[{"id":"c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7","name":"毛远新在批邓、反击右倾翻案风斗争中的一些言论（摘编）（1976.11）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"img","author":"毛远新，1976.11，反攻倒算材料","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7/1.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7/2.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7/3.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7/4.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7/5.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7/6.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7/7.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7/8.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7/9.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7/10.png"}],"authors":[{"id":"b7ad58134e","name":"毛远新"}]},"publication_details":{"c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7":{"comments":[{"id":"a97f3cd4cf","publicationId":"c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7","articleId":"e71b2f7f0e","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"一九七六年十一月"}],"contents":[{"id":"278b394c67","type":"title","text":"（四）毛远新一九七六年四月十九日谈对当前工作的意见","index":0,"publicationId":"c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7","articleId":"e71b2f7f0e"},{"id":"88217ab8e9","type":"paragraph","text":"关于当前的工作问题，学习主席指示，深入批邓，打击敌人的破坏活动是一致的。当前一个突出特点是敌人用制造、散布反革命谣言，煽动一些人破坏、干扰反击右倾翻案风的斗争，于扰学习和批邓深入，妄图分裂中央，制造反革命事件。","index":1,"publicationId":"c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7","articleId":"e71b2f7f0e"},{"id":"85901b79f3","type":"paragraph","text":"北京、南京等地的活动，显然是有预谋的，辽宁难道就在真空中吗？要抓紧借中央决议和处理天安门事件的东风，狠狠打击阶级敌人的破坏活动，特别是追查反革命谣言，教育干部和群众。","index":2,"publicationId":"c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7","articleId":"e71b2f7f0e"},{"id":"58531ec23d","type":"paragraph","text":"北京已展开群众性的大检举、大揭发，有父亲检举儿子、哥哥把弟弟送到派出所等事迹。追查的过程，也是教育过程（包括去年七、八、九月的谣言）。切不可书生气十足。省委通知刚刚下去，对敌斗争刚刚展开，要充分发动群众，严格区分和正确处理两类不同性质的矛盾，注意掌握政策，有很多事情要做，还要抓一批典型，包括领导机关。这场斗争还没有结束，要有足够警惕，要睁大眼晴，密切注意阶级斗争的动向，他们在天安门前失败了，还会采取新的花样。天安门前的反革命传单除攻击毛主席、党中央外，还特别攻击上海、辽宁和清华、北大。敌人越是骂我们，我们的工作就要做得越好。学习、批邓、打击反革命，工农业生产，人民生活都要做得更好。","index":3,"publicationId":"c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7","articleId":"e71b2f7f0e"},{"id":"93bac86246","type":"paragraph","text":"追查情况要定期报告，千万抓紧（包括军区，去年传的谣言也相当多）。","index":4,"publicationId":"c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7","articleId":"e71b2f7f0e"}],"page":{"id":"4aa4b15cee","publicationId":"c02feeb6-58b4-44b9-9965-47de5504e4b7","articleId":"e71b2f7f0e","start":7,"end":8}}}},"__N_SSG":true}